192
00:10:39.930 --> 00:10:42.540
Agent 365 is natively integrated

193
00:10:42.540 --> 00:10:45.540
out of the box with
these platforms.

194
00:10:45.540 --> 00:10:50.040
It doesn't matter if you are
no-code, low-code or pro-code,

195
00:10:50.040 --> 00:10:54.150
when makers and developers build
on Microsoft AI platforms,

196
00:10:54.150 --> 00:10:57.570
the agent shows up in
Agent 365 automatically.

197
00:10:57.570 --> 00:10:59.580
Identity, observability,
governance,

198
00:10:59.580 --> 00:11:02.220
and security are all wired in.

199
00:11:02.220 --> 00:11:04.530
JEREMIAH FOLLIS: So, yeah, I
mean, that's a clean story

200
00:11:04.530 --> 00:11:05.700
for the Microsoft side.

201
00:11:05.700 --> 00:11:07.380
Would like you to flip
it on me, though.

202
00:11:07.380 --> 00:11:11.820
Say I'm a developer building on
a different platform entirely,

203
00:11:11.820 --> 00:11:15.540
how does Agent 365 reach
my agent in that case?

204
00:11:15.540 --> 00:11:17.640
SUNIL GARG: Yep, that's
a good question.

205
00:11:17.640 --> 00:11:20.850
So Agent 365 already
connects directly

206
00:11:20.850 --> 00:11:23.880
to leading third-party
platforms like Vertex AI

