214
00:11:44.940 --> 00:11:45.270
JEREMIAH FOLLIS: And what

215
00:11:45.270 --> 00:11:47.610
about developers building
their own agents

216
00:11:47.610 --> 00:11:49.920
with an SDK or framework?

217
00:11:49.920 --> 00:11:54.420
OpenAI's SDK, LangChain,
Claude, custom code.

